<br>
I can tell you that the one time Lod did pop, Staboo was VERY concerned about who had aggro first.  It became his whole case when he did not get the kill.  As soon as Lod went down he started screaming that the Map piece was his cause he had engaged first. <br>
<br>
I would rephrase that - All of his little group was dead when we ran over and Lodizal was about 3 secs away from murdering Stab.  So we saved his ass by getting the kite on.  The folks who got the kill that time put the ring and spells up for all to roll on, i thought that was more then generous.  But that didnt stop Staboo accusing everyone present of KSing AND ninja looting.  Whatever, it was a fun fight.<br>
<br>
As the days progressed, Staboo's tactics started to change as he realized the spawn realy was FFA and he was not gonna just be awarded a piece of loot casue he was sitting there 24/7.  He started recruiting exclusively rangers and rogues.  I guess relying on the other teams present to slow and heal and take all the punishment, while he could KS.<br>
<br>
My favorate Staboo quote, &quot;Why dont you guys CAMP HIM like yer supposed to, instead of just showing up when u THINK hes gonna spawn?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Um, cause we have jobs and lives and stuff?&quot;<br>
<br>
He and his high level ranger buddy (not you tynan) threatened our team (2 whole groups) that they would petition us if we even LOOKED at Lodizal.  <br>
<br>
Staboo is one of those young players who is pretty well geared up and no one can figure out how or why.  He manages to piss off just about everyone he comes into contact with, yet still claims to have these mysterious friends who are helping him out.<br>
<br>
If you are one of these friends, stop it already!  You are creating a monster who expects everything will be just handed to him.<br>
<br>
For a while i guess he was pleadging to LC before they got wise.  And today, he could be very publicly seen in Kael, kissing VM's ass when Tormax got ninja looted.  I asked a few of my vis friends about him and they too said he was an annoyance.<br>
<br>
Way too much Staboo in my life these days.  Just plz go back to Karnors and stay there till you get a clue.  Give the higher lev zones a break pretty plz.  /ignore Staboo<br>
<br>
Point of order.  Did anyone see the latest Issue of MAXIM?  In it there is an article on EQ.  They interview a GM who talks about the Lodizal spawn and how it is a CONFIRMED FFA spawn.  So if you get the kill, you decide who gets the loot.  Hopefully someone with a shred of decency would allow some public rolling.  But its not required.  It's PUBLISHED!!  Heh<br>
